{"id": "1370085479294439455", "channel_id": "1367469935894466621", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229>", "timestamp": "2025-05-08T17:10:33.221000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1367469935894466621", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」《無bug空間的逆襲 ～ 一度被稱為bug空間的我逆活一世，在維修公告拿出證明自己無bug的真本事 ～》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1370070483533303899", "channel_id": "1370070483533303899", "type": 0, "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "author_bot": false, "content": "When using Corposant's Overexalt, due to it triggering Aftershock 2 times, you would expect the cost of any Lightning Retribution cards in hand to be reduced 2 times due to the Prepare 1 tag on the card.\n\nHowever, this does not happen and the cost is only reduced by 1, same as with any other discard/draw effect. Is this intended? If it is intended behavior, honestly it makes the Overexalt very situational and not as impactful as you might expect it to be.\n\n[DeepSeek] <:takenotes:1357186646294138890> \n使用「Corposant」的「Overexalt」時，由於它會觸發兩次「Aftershock」，而卡牌上的「Prepare 1」標籤理應讓手牌中任何「Lightning Retribution」的費用降低兩次。\n\n然而，實際情況並非如此，費用僅減少了1次，與其他棄牌/抽牌效果相同。這是設計上的預期行為嗎？如果是的話，坦白說這會讓「Overexalt」變得非常情境化，效果也不如預期中那麼顯著。", "timestamp": "2025-05-08T16:10:57.953000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370070483533303899", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Corposant Overexalt Lightning Retribution Bug?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168939622727801", "1361168893200044183"]}
