{"id": "1369951164711440464", "channel_id": "1369951164711440464", "type": 0, "author_id": "484555315447332864", "author_name": "randomplayer852", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前隨著角色增多，需求不同的密契，以及不同的屬性，配套的密契也越來越多。\n可不可以考慮按照密契约類型排序方便玩家選擇？", "timestamp": "2025-05-08T08:16:50.129000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-08T09:30:35.342000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1369951165202300948", "filename": "IMG_4131.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1131289, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1369951164711440464/1369951165202300948/IMG_4131.png?ex=69cc2bb2&is=69cada32&hm=f60a2bfb9e8151172fc4aeffad27fa6e2d140549d3c4e27eab63f336be3fc983&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1369951164711440464", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "有沒有考慮出個命輪排序功能", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
